<?xml version="1.0"?>
<ruleset name="Team OS PHPMD rule set"
		 xmlns="http://pmd.sf.net/ruleset/1.0.0"
		 xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
		 xsi:schemaLocation="http://pmd.sf.net/ruleset/1.0.0
					 http://pmd.sf.net/ruleset_xml_schema.xsd"
		 xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="
					 http://pmd.sf.net/ruleset_xml_schema.xsd">
	<description>
		* Static methods are forbidden

		* CyclomaticComplexity is set to 10
		* NPathComplexity is set 200
		* ExcessiveMethodLength is set 25 with ignored whitespaces
		* ExcessiveClassLength is set 250 with ignored whitespaces

		* Superglobals variables are forbidden
		* Use CamelCase

		* exit, eval, goto, var_dump, print functions are forbidden
		* NumberOfChildren is set to 15
		* DepthOfInheritance is set to 6
		* Number of acceptable dependencies is set to 15

		* Minimum variable name is set to 3 characters, except: id,e,i,x,y,ip
		* Maximum variable name is set to 25 characters
		* Constructor name must be __construct
		* Constants must be uppercase

		* Any unused variable or method is not allowed
	</description>
